cite-bracket">[</span>2<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span></a></sup></li>
<li><b>hyperbolic cosine</b> "<span class=3D"texhtml">cosh</span>" (<span c=
lass=3D"rt-commentedText nowrap"><span class=3D"IPA nopopups noexcerpt" lan=
g=3D"en-fonipa"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA/English" =
