<p>The hyperbolic tangent is the (unique) solution to the <a href=3D"https:=
//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Differential_equation" title=3D"Differential equati=
on">differential equation</a> <span class=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>=E2=80=89=E2=
=80=B2 =3D 1 =E2=88=92 <i>f</i>=E2=80=89<sup>2</sup></span>, with <span cla=
ss=3D"texhtml"><i>f</i>=E2=80=8A(0) =3D 0</span>.<sup id=3D"cite_ref-18" cl=
ass=3D"reference"><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperbolic_funct=
ions#cite_note-18"><span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>18<span class=3D"ci=
te-bracket">]</span></a></sup><sup id=3D"cite_ref-19" class=3D"reference"><=
a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperbolic_functions#cite_note-19">=
<span class=3D"cite-bracket">[</span>19<span class=3D"cite-bracket">]</span=
></a></sup>
</p>
